A Comprehensive History of C S S, Institutions, Specs, and Practice.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.000
Executive Summary. C S S, Cascading Style Sheets, has evolved through parallel tracks:

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.000
the formal progression of W three C specifications and the informal ways developers actually used C S S in practice.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.000
Over nearly three decades, these tracks have continually influenced each other.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.000
Key phases include: Early Standards: C S S was born from the need to separate content from presentation on the Web.

