00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.000
with the novel idea of blending author and user styles,

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.000
led to C S S Level one in one thousand nine hundred and ninety six.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.000
Early adoption was slow due to limited browser support and a perception that C S S could only handle basic styling.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.000
Pioneering sites like C S S Zen Garden dramatically demonstrated C S S's potential by using one H T M L file with multiple C

